BLIST.TITLE: In order to know which versions of Selenium support a given version of Chrome
BLIST.ITEM:
Look at https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.seleniumhq.selenium/selenium-devtools-v118https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.seleniumhq.selenium/selenium-devtools-v118
enHTML where 118 is replaced by the Chrome version.
The versions (e.g. 4.15.0) correspond to the version ofe selenium-java artefact containing it.
